      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Discover Your Free Phones</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>3. Companies That Offer Smartphones</h4>\n<p>Many companies provide free smartphones, including <a href=\"https://phone.uslowcosthousing.com/provider/access-wireless/\">Access Wireless</a>, <a href=\"https://phone.uslowcosthousing.com/provider/assurance-wireless/\">Assurance Wireless</a>, <a href=\"https://phone.uslowcosthousing.com/provider/american-assistance/\">American Assistance</a>, <a href=\"https://phone.uslowcosthousing.com/provider/life-wireless/\">Life Wireless</a>, <a href=\"https://phone.uslowcosthousing.com/provider/q-link-wireless/\">QLink Wireless</a>, <a href=\"https://phone.uslowcosthousing.com/provider/terracom-wireless/\">Terracom Wireless</a>, <a href=\"https://phone.uslowcosthousing.com/provider/t-mobile/\">T-Mobile</a>, <a href=\"https://phone.uslowcosthousing.com/provider/us-connect/\">U.S. Connect</a>, <a href=\"https://phone.uslowcosthousing.com/provider/att-mobility/\">ATT Mobility</a>, and more. </p>\n<img alt=\"Discover Your Free Phones_4\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/discover-your-free-phones/discover-your-free-phones_4.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/discover-your-free-phones/discover-your-free-phones_4.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/discover-your-free-phones/discover-your-free-phones_4.we